Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從未感受過陽光照在我臉上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未呼吸過真正的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未在水中漂浮過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都從未試過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整三代以來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方舟維持了剩下的人類的生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今  我們的家園瀕臨毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們  是人類最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100個人被派往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行一項孤注一擲的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這的每個人都是因為違反過法律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而地球上  沒有法律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要做的只有生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們將接受考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受地球的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受這里所隱藏的秘密的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是  接受相互的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《地球百子》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-鎮定  -對他們來說我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經死了  沒人在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議會在表決是否要處決300人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以節省氧氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無線電丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽求你了  讓我去找個醫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  你不能告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我如果有人知道了會怎樣  說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會被流放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要第二個孩子有什么錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方舟不可能永遠維持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以法官不能允許
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像奧古斯都大帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像書里寫的那個皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子要出來了  拿毯子來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有個妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她起個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧古斯都大帝也有個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧克塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉米  讓她別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  媽  你不能睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽  我該怎么做  媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出聲  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  我說過了吧  沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你受到傷害的  奧克塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧克塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著方舟上幾百個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就要死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人難以入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文的燃燒棒會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無線電的成功幾率肯定更大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到奧克塔維亞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  不過那是奧克塔維亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能出去追蝴蝶什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克  我找了整個營地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我會幫你找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去看運輸船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去營地里其他地方找找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別謝我  我這么做不是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了奧克塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  求求你別傷害我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你別  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要  求你了  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙兒  都過來拿把武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹獨自在外已經12個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都武裝起來  找不到她絕不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈斯珀  你沒必要這么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把你帶回來之后你還沒出過營地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克  我必須這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要用上所有的人手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要一個追蹤者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬  快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想少一只耳朵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不能相信你在監獄里留了這么長的頭發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等到早上再剪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然來了靈感  所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和我聊什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉上的表情可不是"沒什么"的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是"我要去太空漫步"的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證不會再去太空漫步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休息吧  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬  我們得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我就來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發型不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得談談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有女朋友了  芬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什么可說的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意雷文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你和我  我們擦出過火花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么不能終止的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙兒們  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見那個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒棒沒起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒看見那些燃燒棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道從一場流星雨你就看出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是流星雨  那是葬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾百具尸體從方舟上被送回了地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地球上看來就像是流星雨一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒收到我們的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你找到了無線電
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你把它從我艙里偷走且毀了它之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  他清楚這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且從現在開始他得背負這后果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道我妹妹還在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我必須找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來還是不來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們還等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得和他們取得聯系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,300人不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧氣量會不斷下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我們不告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上是可以生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會殺掉更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他們別無選擇  -伙計們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要走了  咱們得動身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該留下來修好無線電  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么修  發送器都砸碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非有零件空降下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我們無法和方舟對話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術品補給店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有個地方也許能給你弄到發送器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來你要和我一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬  沒有你我們找不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他給縫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那  你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是奧克塔維亞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們需要繩子爬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手電筒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下到底下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有別人在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那邊的印記更深一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他帶走了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們帶走了她  那她還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們帶走我的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂地球語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我可以肯定這意味著禁止入內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-咱們走吧  -簡直瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹  我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是下地獄  我也要找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得咱們已經下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要再騎一次小馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要騎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你想穿過叢林野地還是森林
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看方舟  貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我帶出門去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊媽媽  告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么不會被突擊檢查突擊到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管好你自己  貝拉米·布萊克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你妹妹如果被他們找到會發生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道會發生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴過她幾千遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道該怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨這事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我真希望自己沒被生出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口  奧克塔維亞  我知道你害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而恐懼是個魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛  然后告訴你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能把惡魔殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門  臨檢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻開門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊克女士  我們受議會之命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這進行一次隨機檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格魯斯檢察官  很高興見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的制服已經補好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  跟新的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么東西要給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉米的推薦信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子  你認為你是當警衛的料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這來  讓我好好看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-站起來  快點  -我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想不想當警衛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我數三個數  趕緊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉米  對不起  檢察官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我  -不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許當警衛能使他成長為一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把它收拾干凈  -是  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  這個房間沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒到我的住處來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就給你他的推薦信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕  我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文  我知道你昨天才到這
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們可沒時間賞花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊時間拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你媽媽真像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她一點兒都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張  我是夸獎你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾比可厲害了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個吊艙就是她的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和我一起下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定特別傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她一直都相信你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  她真是年度好媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽幾乎從來沒有陪伴過我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她一無所有的時候才會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會生下我肯定是為了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿我的配給去換酒喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你靠什么生存
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居家的男孩  芬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把他那份配給分給我  記得我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到蹤跡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣漫無目的地找不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該原路返回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才還在這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分開找  他不可能走遠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們藏在樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不應該越界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們試試這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么找到這個地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我找到的  是芬找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RF  無線電頻率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能找到控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看到只雙頭鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在第一天到地球上的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到天堂  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意外中發現美好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去拯救世界  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我們可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該怎么辦  他們一直追著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會為了他停下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們知道她在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪格斯  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  羅瑪  可能還有  快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們把我們引到這里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能跑進這里來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追羅瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對猜不到接下來有什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查唄  我要進洞了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  坐下  坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  貝爾  我不想再聽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么美妙的月出了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠都不能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.09,0:24:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團結日化裝舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分鐘后開始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.09,0:24:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  本來我什么都不想說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.24,0:24:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我確定我的實習組
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.62,0:24:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責安保工作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在那里看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由始至終
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還不是守衛呢  實習生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.29,0:24:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.89,0:24:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘莫測
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾  媽媽怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能別擔心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒等她發現你出去  我們就已經回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.85,0:25:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去走走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.21,0:25:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.36,0:27:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.72,0:27:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個不會注意到我們的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.96,0:27:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.09,0:27:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.94,0:28:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.25,0:28:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個女孩  我認識
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.64,0:28:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她在這里  那我哥哥一定也在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.22,0:28:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你也幫幫他  他們會殺了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.15,0:28:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽不懂我說話  對嗎  好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.46,0:28:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么要照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.58,0:29:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在山澗底下發現的我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.41,0:29:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好我的膝蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.60,0:29:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.60,0:29:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.29,0:29:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下  拜托  請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.82,0:29:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在這  羅瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.50,0:29:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們耍我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.97,0:29:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是因為我才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們愿意  隨時可以殺死我們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.64,0:30:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊的來個干脆的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.21,0:30:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.36,0:30:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道你們在那
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.67,0:30:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想殺我們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.01,0:30:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.53,0:30:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個霧角  是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.81,0:30:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸霧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.74,0:30:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.34,0:30:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.33,0:30:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.03,0:30:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪個站的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.22,0:31:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽耀斑預警
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.04,0:31:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個X級太陽耀斑已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在方舟的右舷
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.29,0:31:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有公民必須立刻至最近的避難區報到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.84,0:31:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是演習  這是太陽耀斑預警
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.40,0:31:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾  我得回家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.90,0:31:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們  你們知道該怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.00,0:31:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘掉面具  出示身份證
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.12,0:31:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾  我們該怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.66,0:31:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  無論發生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.23,0:31:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都得跑回家藏到地板下面
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.29,0:31:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里  你會一如既往地安全的 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.43,0:31:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.69,0:31:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來掩護你  快
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.58,0:31:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾  我該怎么回家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.94,0:31:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實習生布萊克  為何亮出武器
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.45,0:31:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘掉面具
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.62,0:31:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  她沒事  我已經檢查過她了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.92,0:32:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒有掃描器
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.53,0:32:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請出示身份證
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.51,0:32:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  沙姆韋中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.92,0:32:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  放她走
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.92,0:32:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為您的守衛同事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.19,0:32:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我們離開
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.24,0:32:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.27,0:32:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.31,0:32:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  出示身份證
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.44,0:32:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攔住她
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.45,0:32:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.47,0:32:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這管用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.81,0:32:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.14,0:32:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.45,0:32:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有霧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.69,0:32:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是假警報
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.43,0:32:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.45,0:33:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.12,0:33:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在能跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.28,0:33:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看不到我們  我要跟著他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.19,0:33:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.07,0:33:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.51,0:33:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼他說出奧克塔維亞在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.26,0:33:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.72,0:33:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎么知道他不會把我們領向另一個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.13,0:33:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.14,0:33:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.09,0:33:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.56,0:33:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地堡回來的一路上你都沒怎么說話
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.81,0:33:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-雷文  -告訴我我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.52,0:34:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我芬沒給你做這個
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.65,0:34:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我在我冒生命危險下來這里時
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.60,0:34:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒在搞我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.63,0:34:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.01,0:34:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也為我做了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.36,0:34:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可一點不特別
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.75,0:34:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我想這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.95,0:34:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至不知道你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.75,0:34:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以為你已經死了  雷文
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.77,0:34:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以為你沒來得及逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.46,0:34:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.37,0:34:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有方舟上我們認識的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.94,0:34:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒辦法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.39,0:34:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅十天  他本可以多等幾天的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.97,0:34:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愛他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.03,0:35:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我壓根不怎么了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.54,0:36:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-貝拉米  -奧克塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.16,0:36:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拿鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.83,0:36:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門羅  守好入口
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.12,0:36:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.73,0:36:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見習生布萊克
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.04,0:36:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是門衛布萊克了  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.64,0:37:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指揮官  這一年發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.56,0:37:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.38,0:37:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你親自把我媽媽流放
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.84,0:37:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還敢到這兒來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.55,0:37:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是聽命行事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.49,0:37:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我到底有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.69,0:37:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是名優秀的士兵  貝拉米  你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.00,0:37:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機靈  勤奮  足智多謀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.75,0:37:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不是名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.69,0:37:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你是這么說的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.90,0:37:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也說了你會不惜一切代價保護你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.91,0:37:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也記得
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.62,0:37:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望這話還有效
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.54,0:37:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.04,0:37:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下面要告訴你的是機密事項
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.47,0:37:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞哈法官批準了一項
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.76,0:37:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重返地球的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.19,0:37:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要把青少年囚犯派往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.58,0:37:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共計一百人  你妹妹也在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.04,0:37:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不能這么做  這不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.12,0:37:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.26,0:37:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.95,0:37:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能給你在運輸船上安排一個座位
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.83,0:37:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.85,0:38:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子很難生還
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.49,0:38:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.43,0:38:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少奧克塔維亞不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.03,0:38:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.96,0:38:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了法官
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.21,0:38:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我現在就把你殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.69,0:38:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我  你妹妹就得獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.95,0:38:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往輻射遍地的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.55,0:38:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你會像你母親一樣被流放
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.86,0:38:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛船二十分鐘后出發  貝拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.46,0:38:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你答應  我們得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.44,0:38:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.96,0:38:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么找到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.02,0:38:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟蹤他找來的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.93,0:38:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧  在他醒來之前快走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.34,0:38:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓他醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.91,0:38:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉米  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.31,0:38:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有傷害我  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.86,0:39:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這戰爭是他們先挑起的  芬  讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.82,0:39:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧角
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.62,0:39:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  那是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.06,0:39:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克  克拉克在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.67,0:39:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.54,0:39:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.38,0:39:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧克塔維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.84,0:39:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬  芬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.10,0:39:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天吶  天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.46,0:39:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.61,0:39:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.62,0:39:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉米不讓我把刀拔出來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.02,0:39:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.40,0:39:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他帶到運輸船去  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.67,0:39:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克  你能救他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.11,0:39:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不不行  得讓我媽媽幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.14,0:39:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得和她溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.49,0:39:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但無線電不能用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.54,0:39:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文  修好它  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.66,0:40:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.40,0:40:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才為什么護著他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.98,0:40:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他救了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.16,0:40:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺中羅瑪的長矛其實是用來...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.14,0:40:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你搞錯了  是我救了你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.80,0:40:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道  他把你救活
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.11,0:40:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了拿你當活誘
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.00,0:40:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不覺得他會這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.71,0:40:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得...  這就是問題所在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.64,0:40:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們今天殺了三個我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.60,0:40:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你當時不阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.78,0:40:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我把他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.76,0:40:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬現在也不會生命垂危了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.76,0:40:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把你的錯都安到我頭上來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.39,0:40:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬的遭遇不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.52,0:40:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時想盡快離開  如果芬死在那
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.51,0:40:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.89,0:40:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.57,0:40:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.07,0:40:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害我被鎖在方舟上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.79,0:40:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我去那該死的舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.02,0:40:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你害媽媽被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.99,0:40:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.65,0:41:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽會被流放是因為生了你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.88,0:41:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會死是因為你活著
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.57,0:41:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.81,0:41:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無從選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.60,0:41:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你出生那天我的人生就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.52,0:41:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.75,0:41:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能永遠把我鎖在這
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.66,0:41:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回營地去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.65,0:41:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.43,0:41:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風暴將至
